{
  "page": "Maid of the seas",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:HBO_Lys_season_2_Prince_maid_of_field_and_seas.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2c/HBO_Lys_season_2_Prince_maid_of_field_and_seas.png/350px-HBO_Lys_season_2_Prince_maid_of_field_and_seas.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"583\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2c/HBO_Lys_season_2_Prince_maid_of_field_and_seas.png/525px-HBO_Lys_season_2_Prince_maid_of_field_and_seas.png 1.5x, /images/2/2c/HBO_Lys_season_2_Prince_maid_of_field_and_seas.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:HBO_Lys_season_2_Prince_maid_of_field_and_seas.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Pentos\" title=\"Prince of Pentos\">Prince of Pentos</a> with the <a href=\"/index.php/Maid_of_the_fields\" title=\"Maid of the fields\">maid of the fields</a> and the maid of the seas, as depicted in <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a>: Histories &amp; Lore</i>.</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>maid of the seas</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> or <b>maid of the sea</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_pentos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_pentos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> is a title given to a young <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden\" title=\"Maiden\">maiden</a> of the Free City of <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a>. Every year a new maid of the seas is chosen.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"About\">About</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maid_of_the_seas&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: About\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>On the first day of each new year, the <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Pentos\" title=\"Prince of Pentos\">Prince of Pentos</a> deflowers the <a href=\"/index.php/Maid_of_the_fields\" title=\"Maid of the fields\">maid of the fields</a> and the maid of the seas.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_pentos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_pentos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> This ancient ritual, which may arise from the mysterious origins of pre-<a href=\"/index.php/Valyria\" title=\"Valyria\">Valyrian</a> Pentos, is meant to ensure the continued prosperity of Pentos on land and at sea.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_pentos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_pentos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maid_of_the_seas&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_1\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 1\">Chapter 1</a>, Tyrion I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_pentos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_pentos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_pentos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_pentos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Free Cities: Pentos.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403151208\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.020 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.021 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 428/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8680/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1553/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 433/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2028/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   13.397      1 -total\n 81.02%   10.854      5 Template:Ref\n 48.70%    6.525      5 Template:Ref/core\n 15.48%    2.074      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:24358-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403151208 a